    • Uses of Command in zombietask

      Subclasses of Command in zombietask 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  CommandAdd
      Class for Add command, which contains task name, date and time, a list of tags and boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.
      class  CommandAddFloating
      Class for Add Floating Task command, which contains task name, a list of tags and boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.
      class  CommandAddTimed
      Class for Add Timed Task command, which contains task name, 2 sets of date and time, a list of tags and boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.
      class  CommandDelete
      Class for Delete command, which contains line number to identify task to delete, and a boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.
      class  CommandHelp
      Class for Help command, which contains a string to indicate type of view and a boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.
      class  CommandSearchName
      Class for Search Name command, which contains a search string and a boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.
      class  CommandSearchTime
      Class for Search Time command, which contains 2 sets of date and time and a boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.
      class  CommandUpdate
      Class for Update command, which contains line number to identify task to update, and a boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.
      class  CommandView
      Class for View command, which contains a string to indicate type of view and a boolean variable to indicate missing arguments.

      Parses the user input and returns a command object containing the command type and its arguments
